cracy promotion and rule of law applicants working at the intersection of two or more of these issue areas will receive preferential consideration the center expects to award three to four fellowships for the 2012 13 academic year for additional information about the program and application procedures please visit our fellowship page at http cddrl stanford edu fellowships cddrl_fellowships applications are due by january 31 2012 cddrl pre doctoral and postdoctoral fellowships fellowship for graduate students postdoctoral scholars not accepting applications at this time pdf+ search cddrl search within everything courses events fellowships news op eds people publications research other pages news of interest applications for summer fellowships open october 14 2011 phr announcement announcing the 2011 12 pre and post doctoral fellows april 27 2011 news cddrl accepting applications to senior honors program january 25 2011 announcement postdoctoral fellowships for program on global justice november 23 2010 pgj announcement cddrl hewlett fellowships now accepting applications november 3 2009 draper hills summer fellows program announcement program on global justice center for ethics in society seek postdoctoral fellows for 2009 2010 october 30 2008 pgj announcement support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 723 4610 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
